data.title: Farewell Wreathlaying Ceremony for retiring Chief of Army Lieutenant General Ken Gillespie
data.meta_description:
Farewell Wreathlaying Ceremony for retiring Chief of Army Lieutenant General Ken Gillespie, AC, DSC, CSM, held in the Hall of Memory on Monday 27 June 2011. 
	
	General Gillespie gave his final salute in front of the Tomb of the Unknown Australian Soldier. These photos are from that special ceremony.
data.text:
Farewell Wreathlaying Ceremony for retiring Chief of Army Lieutenant General Ken Gillespie, AC, DSC, CSM, held in the Hall of Memory on Monday 27 June 2011.

General Gillespie gave his final salute in front of the Tomb of the Unknown Australian Soldier. These photos are from that special ceremony.
